text: Our Lady of Egypt is a Roman Catholic church in Kalina, Mumbai under the Archdiocese of Bombay. The church was founded in 1606 and celebrated its 400th anniversary in mid-2006. Its current parish priest is Father Rui Comelo. ==References== Category:Roman Catholic churches in Mumbai Category:Roman Catholic churches in Maharashtra Category:1606 establishments in India Category:Religious organizations established in the 1600s Category:Catholic congregations established in the 17th century
